phase2.explanation:
🤖 **Common dispatcher mistakes and fixes.**

| Mistake | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| Heavy work on main | Use `Dispatchers.Default` |
| IO on main | Use `Dispatchers.IO` |
| No result handling | Show loading/result |

**Fixes:**
```kotlin
// 1. Use Default dispatcher
withContext(Dispatchers.Default) {
    // Heavy computation
}

// 2. Use IO dispatcher
withContext(Dispatchers.IO) {
    // Network/database
}

// 3. Handle result
var isLoading by remember { mutableStateOf(false) }
var result by remember { mutableStateOf("") }

Button(onClick = {
    isLoading = true
    viewModel.doAsyncWork()
}) {
    if (isLoading) CircularProgressIndicator()
    else Text("Load")
}
```

